##### Otter: Keep /dist tracked; ignore build/vcpkg caches; Rust runner target ignored except exe pinned by path rule if desired.
##### Schneefuchs: Specific rules after general ones; Windows-friendly; no surprises.
##### Maus: Minimal, readable; comments explain intent.
##### Datei: .gitignore

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Build trees (local)
build/
build-*/

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# vcpkg work dirs & caches (local only)
vcpkg/
vcpkg_installed/
vcpkg_cache/

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# VS / IDE metadata
*.suo
*.user
*.VC.db
.vscode/*
!.vscode/c_cpp_properties.json
!.vscode/settings.json
.idea/
.vs/

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# CMake generator files
CMakeFiles/
CMakeCache.txt
cmake_install.cmake
Makefile
compile_commands.json

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Common temporaries
*.log
*.tmp
*.bak
*~
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Compiled artifacts (we stage selected ones into /dist)
*.obj
*.o
*.lib
*.dll
*.exe
*.pdb
*.dmp
*.ilk

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Keep /dist in the repo (staged outputs live here)
!dist/
!dist/**

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Rust: ignore generic target trees globally, keep sources
target/
!rust/
!rust/otter_proc/
!rust/otter_proc/**

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Project-specific
imgui.ini
wupp.txt

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Archives
*.zip
*.7z
OtterDream_Project.zip
